init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I began to feel a bit uneasy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was in a place I didn't know, with people I didn't know.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I didn't know what was going to happen to me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I saw a man who looked like me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Can you tell me where I am?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You died, and now you're watching your next life."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I turned around, and saw a man in a suit, with a badge that said "Security".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I ran as fast as I could, and I didn't look back.
